metadata.name: The Collector
metadata.description: Sergey, also known as Merlin, is a seasoned photographer and light painting specialist. Over a decade, he honed his technique and now creates stunning artworks on special blanks and mannequins. Introduced to NFTs by his Instagram followers in late 2021, Sergey has embraced this medium to showcase his mesmerizing art. As a passionate promoter of light painting, he's joined the JRNY Collective to share his unique vision. We're thrilled to welcome Merlin and look forward to showcasing his extraordinary journey in light painting. - https://linktr.ee/lightpaintings
